WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.500
Step 1: Create an Agent

00:01.500 --> 00:03.000
Define name, model, system instructions, tools, and parameters.

00:03.000 --> 00:04.500
Step 2: Test the Agent

00:04.500 --> 00:06.000
Stream responses, approve tool calls with human-in-the-loop.

00:06.000 --> 00:07.500
Step 3: Create a Workflow

00:07.500 --> 00:09.000
Add ordered steps, attach agents, enable approvals.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.500
Step 4: Run & Monitor

00:10.500 --> 00:12.000
Review streaming logs, approvals, final status and usage.
